<div class="content">
  <h1>The OSS Survival Game</h1>
  <p>status: in-development</p>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p>The OSS Survival Game is a game where you survive from people and viruses whilst trying to survive on water and energy bars. The game was intended to be the Michael Jackson's: Musical Stars game but was retextured to be an OSS game. The re-texture was done to avoid getting NFE'd or banned on Scratch due to blood, medicine, death, and more.<br><br>How to play:<br>Collect tin cans, cardboard boxes, trash bags, duffle bags, and cups to get 1 random item from an apple, to a Pepsee. You can only hold 1 item, so when you grab one of the bags, you drop the item in the item box. You have 4 stats to keep in control, HEALTH, THIRST, ANGER, and RICHES, make sure to keep HEALTH over 15, THIRST over 0, ANGER over 50, and RICHES over 100. When you get too angry or thirsty, your health will deplete by the second. When you are too rich, people will try to rob you of your items and riches. When health gets too low, your vision is obstructed by "kool-aid". GAME IS NOT FINALIZED SO THESE ARE SUBJECT TO CHANGE.</p><br><h3>Controls</h3><p>PC<br>P to open and close Phone<br><br>MOBILE<br>NOT FINALIZED</p><br><br>
</div>

